<p>We have released BJCA Global CP/CPS v1.0.4 on June 23, 2021.<br>
In section 4.9.12 of the CPS, the method used by that parties to demonstrate private key compromise is clearly specified.<br>
The updated documents can be found in our repository: <a href="https://www.bjca.cn/cps" rel="nofollow">https://www.bjca.cn/cps</a><br>
Here is BJCA Global CPS v1.0.4: <a href="https://www.bjca.cn/cps/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99.pdf" rel="nofollow">https://www.bjca.cn/cps/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD%E6%9C%89%E9%99%90%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E4%BD%93%E7%B3%BB%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%81%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1%E8%A7%84%E5%88%99.pdf</a></p>
